WHAS Staff, WHAS11.com 7:47 a.m. EDT October 16, 2015 Rachel Platten will be performing on 4th Street Live! at the Hard Rock Cafe. (Photo: WHAS 11) CONNECT TWEET   
LOUISVILLE, Ky (WHAS11) -- Musician Rachel Platten will rocking out this Friday night at the Hard Rock Cafe on 4th Street Live! 
The pop stars first hit "Fight Song" has reached number six on the Billboard charts. Platten began her career in 2003 with her first album ' Trust in Me'. 
Her concert will start at 8 p.m.  //on.whas11.com/1LxgS9S More Stories
